      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed weekly. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a premium ceramic coating that makes the finish pop, entirely free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that fresh, new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a full folder of documented service history exclusively from authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
